Package: gaezv5
Type: Package
Title: Download and Process GAEZ v5 Agricultural Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Julian", "Joseph",
           email = "joseph@iiasa.ac.at",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3844-7807")),
    person("IIASA", role = "cph")
    )
Description: Tools for downloading and working with Global Agro-Ecological Zones
    (GAEZ) version 5 data from the Food and Agriculture Organization (FAO).
    GAEZ v5 provides comprehensive global data on agricultural potential, crop
    suitability, attainable yields, and agro-climatic resources. This package
    simplifies data access through intuitive functions for searching variables,
    building download URLs, and batch downloading datasets across multiple crops,
    scenarios, and time periods. Features efficient parallel downloads, time series
    support, and flexible parameter handling for climate change impact studies.
